                                                          <p>The times of legends, when humans and gods shared the same world, are long gone, spanning millions of years. During those times, the driving force behind the world&#039;s movements were the aspirations of mankind. The era known as the 500 year war, or the Era of Warring States, was characterized by this. Kingdom tells the tale of a youthful individual who blossomed into a renowned commander and the tumultuous challenges and violent incidents that accompanied his rise. </p>
