                            <div><span class="aye_icon">140,644,390</span></div> <br><br>

                            
                                                          <p>Listen up folks! I’m living my life with the demon queen!   A normal powerless male protagonist is entrusted to look after the fallen demon queen Isabella. Depleted of her powers, Isabella is forced to camouflage as a human and suppress her regal status. Evil masterminds plot to dethrone a powerful demon queen in a medieval fantasy land. </p>
